  "title": "Claron McFadden: Singing the primal mystery",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 20228.0,
      "text": "(Singing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 33830.0,
      "end_time": 34424.0,
      "text": "(Singing ends)"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 138171.0,
      "end_time": 144828.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 146779.0,
      "end_time": 149787.0,
      "text": "Pep Rosenfeld: Folks, you&#39;ve just met Claron McFadden."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 149811.0,
      "end_time": 152398.0,
      "text": "She is a world-class soprano singer"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 152422.0,
      "end_time": 154236.0,
      "text": "who studied in Rochester, New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 154938.0,
      "end_time": 158234.0,
      "text": "Her celebrated operatic roles are numerous and varied."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 158649.0,
      "end_time": 164220.0,
      "text": "In August 2007, Claron was awarded the Amsterdam Prize for the Arts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 164244.0,
      "end_time": 166590.0,
      "text": "winning praise for her brilliance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 166830.0,
      "end_time": 169489.0,
      "text": "her amazing and extensively wide repertoire"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 169513.0,
      "end_time": 171236.0,
      "text": "and her vivid stage personality."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 171704.0,
      "end_time": 173650.0,
      "text": "Please welcome Claron McFadden."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 173674.0,
      "end_time": 180594.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 184660.0,
      "end_time": 186327.0,
      "text": "Claron McFadden: The human voice:"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 187334.0,
      "end_time": 191107.0,
      "text": "mysterious, spontaneous, primal."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 193530.0,
      "end_time": 197990.0,
      "text": "For me, the human voice is the vessel on which all emotions travel --"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 198140.0,
      "end_time": 199927.0,
      "text": "except, perhaps, jealousy."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 201840.0,
      "end_time": 203315.0,
      "text": "And the breath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 203339.0,
      "end_time": 205495.0,
      "text": "the breath is the captain of that vessel."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 207591.0,
      "end_time": 209153.0,
      "text": "A child is born,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 210558.0,
      "end_time": 212201.0,
      "text": "takes its first breath --"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 212863.0,
      "end_time": 216776.0,
      "text": "(Inhales)"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 218100.0,
      "end_time": 219160.0,
      "text": "Whah!"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 220531.0,
      "end_time": 223597.0,
      "text": "And we behold the wondrous beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 224954.0,
      "end_time": 226438.0,
      "text": "of vocal expression --"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 227188.0,
      "end_time": 229810.0,
      "text": "mysterious, spontaneous"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 230899.0,
      "end_time": 232500.0,
      "text": "and primal."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 233923.0,
      "end_time": 237650.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, I did a meditation retreat in Thailand."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 237890.0,
      "end_time": 238542.0,
      "text": "I wanted a place"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 239279.0,
      "end_time": 243236.0,
      "text": "where I would have total silence and total solitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 243988.0,
      "end_time": 246595.0,
      "text": "I spent two weeks at this retreat"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 246619.0,
      "end_time": 248333.0,
      "text": "in my own little hut --"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 248357.0,
      "end_time": 251166.0,
      "text": "no music, no nothing -- sounds of nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 252214.0,
      "end_time": 255753.0,
      "text": "trying to find the essence of concentration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 255777.0,
      "end_time": 257235.0,
      "text": "being in the moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 257937.0,
      "end_time": 259794.0,
      "text": "On my last day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 259817.0,
      "end_time": 261937.0,
      "text": "the woman who looked after the place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 262675.0,
      "end_time": 264851.0,
      "text": "she came and we spoke for a minute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 264875.0,
      "end_time": 266343.0,
      "text": "and then she said to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 267581.0,
      "end_time": 269236.0,
      "text": "\"Would you sing something for me?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 269915.0,
      "end_time": 273192.0,
      "text": "And I thought, but this is a place of total quiet and silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 273216.0,
      "end_time": 274747.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t make noise."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 275810.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "She said, \"Please, sing for me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 279553.0,
      "end_time": 281236.0,
      "text": "So I closed my eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 282180.0,
      "end_time": 283457.0,
      "text": "I took breath"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 285100.0,
      "end_time": 287600.0,
      "text": "and the first thing that came up and out"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 288465.0,
      "end_time": 289861.0,
      "text": "was \"Summertime,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 291370.0,
      "end_time": 292234.0,
      "text": "Porgy and Bess."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 292259.0,
      "end_time": 296402.0,
      "text": "(Singing) Summertime and the livin&#39; is easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 297632.0,
      "end_time": 300774.0,
      "text": "Fish are jumpin&#39; and the cotton is high."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 300798.0,
      "end_time": 304783.0,
      "text": "Oh, your daddy&#39;s rich and your ma is good-lookin&#39;."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 304807.0,
      "end_time": 306397.0,
      "text": "So hush little baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 306421.0,
      "end_time": 308846.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t you cry."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 310103.0,
      "end_time": 311814.0,
      "text": "And I opened my eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 312473.0,
      "end_time": 315236.0,
      "text": "and I saw that she had her eyes closed."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 316100.0,
      "end_time": 318104.0,
      "text": "And after a moment, she opened her eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 318128.0,
      "end_time": 319786.0,
      "text": "and she looked at me and she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 321250.0,
      "end_time": 322662.0,
      "text": "\"It&#39;s like meditation.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 323765.0,
      "end_time": 325986.0,
      "text": "And in that moment I understood"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 326110.0,
      "end_time": 329423.0,
      "text": "that everything I had gone to Thailand to look for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 329447.0,
      "end_time": 331330.0,
      "text": "to search for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 331570.0,
      "end_time": 333452.0,
      "text": "I had it already in my singing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 334866.0,
      "end_time": 337818.0,
      "text": "the calm, but alertness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 338660.0,
      "end_time": 341153.0,
      "text": "the focus, but awareness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 341804.0,
      "end_time": 344613.0,
      "text": "and being totally in the moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 346295.0,
      "end_time": 348410.0,
      "text": "When you&#39;re totally in the moment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 348650.0,
      "end_time": 349564.0,
      "text": "when I&#39;m totally in the moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 349588.0,
      "end_time": 351793.0,
      "text": "the vessel of expression is open."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 351817.0,
      "end_time": 354389.0,
      "text": "The emotions can flow from me"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 354413.0,
      "end_time": 355586.0,
      "text": "to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 355610.0,
      "end_time": 356806.0,
      "text": "and back."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 357817.0,
      "end_time": 359706.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an extremely profound experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 362470.0,
      "end_time": 364397.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a piece by a composer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 364421.0,
      "end_time": 367190.0,
      "text": "an American composer called John Cage."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 367430.0,
      "end_time": 368623.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called \"Aria.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 368647.0,
      "end_time": 373236.0,
      "text": "It was written for an amazing singer called Cathy Berberian."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 373752.0,
      "end_time": 376236.0,
      "text": "And the thing about this piece that&#39;s so special --"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 376942.0,
      "end_time": 378236.0,
      "text": "if you see it behind me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 379267.0,
      "end_time": 381441.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not notated in any way."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 382669.0,
      "end_time": 385359.0,
      "text": "No notes, no flats, no sharps."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 386580.0,
      "end_time": 387804.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s a kind of structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 388431.0,
      "end_time": 390890.0,
      "text": "And the singer, within this structure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 390915.0,
      "end_time": 394935.0,
      "text": "has total freedom to be creative, spontaneous."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 395538.0,
      "end_time": 396689.0,
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 397832.0,
      "end_time": 399379.0,
      "text": "there are different colors"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 399403.0,
      "end_time": 403355.0,
      "text": "and each color gets a different type of singing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 403379.0,
      "end_time": 407268.0,
      "text": "pop, country and western, opera, jazz --"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 407292.0,
      "end_time": 410419.0,
      "text": "and you just have to be consistent with that color."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 411610.0,
      "end_time": 413459.0,
      "text": "You see there are different lines."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 413998.0,
      "end_time": 416205.0,
      "text": "You choose in your own tempo in your own way"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 416229.0,
      "end_time": 417482.0,
      "text": "to follow the line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 417506.0,
      "end_time": 418914.0,
      "text": "but you must respect it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 419726.0,
      "end_time": 420883.0,
      "text": "more or less."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 421391.0,
      "end_time": 422875.0,
      "text": "And these little dots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 423906.0,
      "end_time": 427324.0,
      "text": "these represent a sort of sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 428459.0,
      "end_time": 431236.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s not a vocal, not a lyrical way"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 433467.0,
      "text": "of expressing the voice."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 433491.0,
      "end_time": 435551.0,
      "text": "Using the body -- it could be sneezing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 435576.0,
      "end_time": 437155.0,
      "text": "it could be coughing, animals --"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 437179.0,
      "end_time": 438774.0,
      "text": "(Audience member coughs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 438798.0,
      "end_time": 440900.0,
      "text": "Exactly. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 440114.0,
      "end_time": 441767.0,
      "text": "Clapping, whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 443138.0,
      "end_time": 445104.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s different text."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 445129.0,
      "end_time": 448864.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s Armenian, Russian, French, English, Italian."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 449459.0,
      "end_time": 451967.0,
      "text": "So within this structure, one is free."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 452945.0,
      "end_time": 455548.0,
      "text": "To me, this piece is an ode to the voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 456992.0,
      "end_time": 459540.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s mysterious, as we can see."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 461413.0,
      "end_time": 463550.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s quite spontaneous."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 465811.0,
      "end_time": 467154.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s primal."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 467765.0,
      "end_time": 469955.0,
      "text": "So I would like to share this piece with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 469979.0,
      "end_time": 471929.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s \"Aria,\" of John Cage."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 479528.0,
      "end_time": 480981.0,
      "text": "(Singing in various languages)"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 481500.0,
      "end_time": 485457.0,
      "text": "Hampart-zoum"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 486704.0,
      "end_time": 488200.0,
      "text": "Dirouhi"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 488224.0,
      "end_time": 489953.0,
      "text": "Di questa Terra"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 490605.0,
      "end_time": 494900.0,
      "text": "Naprasno"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 494330.0,
      "end_time": 496176.0,
      "text": "Conscience et"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 496200.0,
      "end_time": 497413.0,
      "text": "(Barks)"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 498581.0,
      "end_time": 505557.0,
      "text": "(Singing) Arise"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 505991.0,
      "end_time": 507140.0,
      "text": "Tsk, tsk, tsk."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 508761.0,
      "end_time": 509895.0,
      "text": "(Singing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 509919.0,
      "end_time": 511853.0,
      "text": "Vidiel’a"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 511877.0,
      "end_time": 514345.0,
      "text": "facilmente"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 514369.0,
      "end_time": 518750.0,
      "text": "E io sono per te"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 519123.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520694.00000000006,
      "text": "(Robotic voice) No other way"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 520717.0,
      "end_time": 522982.0,
      "text": "Dans l&#39;espace, so help"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 524470.0,
      "end_time": 525182.0,
      "text": "(Singing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 525206.0,
      "end_time": 528348.0,
      "text": "Si juste"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 528372.0,
